Generic {{{1
View switching {{{2

Show main view                          m
Show diff view                          d
Show log view                           l
Show reflog view                        L
Show tree view                          t
Show blob view                          f
Show blame view                         b
Show refs view                          r
Show status view                        s  S
Show stage view                         c
Show stash view                         y
Show grep view                          g
Show pager view                         p
Show help view                          h

View manipulation {{{2

Enter and open selected line            «Enter»
Go back to previous view state          <
Move to next                            «Down» «C-n» J
Move to previous                        «Up»   «C-p» K
Move to parent                          ,
Move focus to the next view             «Tab»
Reload and refresh view                 R  «F5»
Maximize the current view               O
Close the current view                  q
Close all views and quit                Q  «C-c»

Cursor navigation {{{2

Move cursor one line up                 k
Move cursor one line down               j
Move cursor one page down               «PageDown»  «SPC»
Move cursor half a page up              «PageUp»  -
Move cursor half a page down            «C-d»
Move cursor one page up                 «C-u»
Move cursor to first line               «Home»
Move cursor to last line                «End»

Scrolling {{{2

Scroll one line up                      «Insert»  «C-y»
Scroll one line down                    «Delete»  «C-e»
Scroll one page up                      «ScrollBack»
Scroll one page down                    «ScrollFwd»
Scroll to the first line columns        |
Scroll two columns left                 «Left»
Scroll two columns right                «Right»

Searching {{{2

Search the view                         /
Search backwards in the view            ?
Find next search match                  n
Find previous search match              N

Misc {{{2

Open in editor                          e
Open the prompt                         :
Open the options menu                   o
Redraw the screen                       «C-l»
Stop all loading views                  z
Show version information                v

Option toggling {{{2

:toggle sort-order                      I
:toggle sort-field                      i
:toggle line-number                     #
:toggle date                            D
:toggle author                          A
:toggle line-graphics                   ~
:toggle file-name                       F
:toggle ignore-space                    W
:toggle id                              X
:toggle commit-title-overflow           $
:toggle file-filter                     %

