Searching {{{2

Find next search match                  «Down» «C-n» «C-j»
Find previous search match              «Up»   «C-p» «C-k»

Main {{{1
Option toggling {{{2

:toggle commit-title-graph              G
:toggle commit-title-refs               F

Internal commands {{{2

:goto HEAD                              H

External commands {{{2

?git cherry-pick %(commit)              C

Diff {{{1
Option toggling {{{2

:toggle diff-context -1                 [
:toggle diff-context +1                 ]

Internal commands {{{2

:/^@@                                   @

Reflog {{{1
Option toggling {{{2

:toggle commit-title-refs               F

External commands {{{2

?git checkout %(branch)                 C
?git reset --hard %(commit)             !

Refs {{{1
External commands {{{2

?git checkout %(branch)                 C
?git branch -D %(branch)                !

Status {{{1
View-specific actions {{{2

Stage/unstage chunk/file changes        u
Revert chunk/file changes               !
Merge file using external tool          M

External commands {{{2

!git commit                             C

Stage {{{1
View-specific actions {{{2

Stage/unstage chunk/file changes        u
Revert chunk/file file changes          !
Stage/unstage single line               1
Split current diff chunk                \

Option toggling {{{2

:toggle diff-context -1                 [
:toggle diff-context +1                 ]

Internal commands {{{2

:/^@@                                   @

Stash {{{1
External commands {{{2

?git stash apply %(stash)               A
?git stash pop %(stash)                 P
?git stash drop %(stash)                !
